---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<PageLayout title="School Holidays">
  <div class="prose-bfs">
    <p>School holiday dates are published in our annual calendars. You can download the current and upcoming academic year calendars below.</p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 my-8">
      <a href="/documents/BFS-Calendar-2025-2026.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary flex items-center gap-2" download>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"/>
        </svg>
        BFS Calendar 2025–2026 (PDF)
      </a>
      <a href="/documents/BFS-Calendar-2026-2027.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-outline flex items-center gap-2" download>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"/>
        </svg>
        BFS Calendar 2026–2027 (PDF)
      </a>
    </div>

    <h2>School Hours</h2>
    <p>
      Mon / Tue / Thu / Fri: <strong>9.15am – 2.15pm</strong><br />
      Wednesday: <strong>10.00am – 3.00pm</strong>
    </p>
    <p>If you have any queries about school holiday dates, please <a href="/contact">contact the school office</a>.</p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
